GAMBIT steering files
=====================


Functionality/configuration demos and minimal examples
------------------------------------------------------

spartan.yaml                                     --- Simplest example of using GAMBIT: a toy-model MultiNest scan
spartan_NUHM1.yaml                               --- Simple example of using GAMBIT in a random scan of NUHM1 params

postprocessor_demo.yaml                          --- Simple example of using the postprocessor scanner to add a new likelihood component

ColliderBit_CMSSM.yaml                           --- LEP and LHC direct search observables in a MultiNest scan of the CMSSM
ColliderBit_ExternalModel.yaml                   --- LHC likelihood demo on a single point of a Pythia external model

DarkBit_MSSM7.yaml                               --- DM constraint demo with a MultiNest scan of the MSSM7 model
DarkBit_ScalarSingletDM_Z2.yaml                  --- DarkBit demo with a simple of MultiNest scan of Singlet DM model

DecayBit_MSSM20.yaml                             --- Test of DecayBit, printing out a decay table for MSSM20 at a single model point
DecayBit_ScalarSingletDM_Z2.yaml                 --- Test of DecayBit, printing out a decay table for Singlet DM at 10 model points

FlavBit_CMSSM.yaml                               --- Flavour physics fits to CMSSM with Diver scan

PrecisionBit_MSSM20.yaml                         --- Precision EW observable demo on a single MSSM20 point

ScannerBit.yaml                                  --- Example of configuring the scanner system

SpecBit_MSSM.yaml                                --- Single-point test of mass spectrum generation in MSSM sub-models
SpecBit_ScalarSingletDM_vacuum_stability.yaml    --- 50x50 grid scan of vacuum stability in [mT,mH]

Mathematica_test.yaml                            --- Simple example demonstrating the use of Mathematica backends
Python_test.yaml                                 --- Simple example demonstrating the use of Python backends

CosmoBit_quickStart.yaml                         --- Quickstart example for CosmoBit
CosmoBit_tutorial.yaml                           --- Tutorial file for using CosmoBit
CosmoBit_Planck_polychord.yaml                   --- Validation of Planck likelihoods with Polychord as sampler

ObjectivesBit_minuit2.yaml                       --- Test of ObjectivesBit, optmising with minuit2


Physics model scan configurations
---------------------------------

CMSSM.yaml                --- Diver scan of CMSSM model
MSSM7.yaml                --- Diver scan of MSSM7 model
MSSM9.yaml                --- Diver scan of MSSM9 model
NUHM1.yaml                --- Diver scan of NUHM1 model
NUHM2.yaml                --- Diver scan of NUHM2 model
ScalarSingletDM_Z2.yaml   --- Diver scan of scalar singlet Higgs-portal DM model with Z2 symmetry
ScalarSingletDM_Z3.yaml   --- Diver scan of scalar singlet Higgs-portal DM model with Z3 symmetry
DiracSingletDM_Z2.yaml    --- Diver scan of Dirac singlet Higgs-portal DM model with Z2 symmetry
MajoranaSingletDM_Z2.yaml --- Diver scan of Majorana singlet Higgs-portal DM model with Z2 symmetry
VectorSingletDM_Z2.yaml   --- Diver scan of Vector singlet Higgs-portal DM model with Z2 symmetry
WC.yaml                   --- MultiNest scan of flavour physics Wilson Coeffs
WC_lite.yaml              --- A lightweight version of WC.yaml, with less observables and parameters
QCDAxions.yaml            --- Scan of a QCD axion model
RHN.yaml                  --- Diver scan of a right-handed neutrino model
DMEFT.yaml                --- Diver scan of the effective field theory of DM


Plotting examples
-----------------
WC_lite.pip               --- plot the results of WC_lite.yaml with pippi
spartan.pip               --- plot the results of spartan.yaml with pippi


Config fragments containing parameters for inclusion in other steering files
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

StandardModel_SLHA2_defaults.yaml                    --- Defaults for StandardModel_SLHA2 parameters
StandardModel_SLHA2_scan.yaml                        --- Defaults for StandardModel_SLHA2 paramaters for MSSM scans
StandardModel_SLHA2_scan_HP.yaml                     --- Defaults for StandardModel_SLHA2 paramaters for HP scans
StandardModel_SLHA2_postprocessing.yaml              --- Defaults for StandardModel_SLHA2 paramaters for postprocessing
StandardModel_SLHA2_Planckbaseline.yaml              --- Defaults for StandardModel_SLHA2 paramaters with Planck baseline for neutrino masses
StandardModel_mNudiff_NH_scan.yaml                   --- Defaults for StandardModel_SLHA2 paramaters with differential neutrino masses in normal hierarchy
StandardModel_mNudiff_IH_scan.yaml                   --- Defaults for StandardModel_SLHA2 paramaters with differential neutrino masses in inverted hierarchy
nuclear_params_ChPT_sigmapiN_fixed.yaml              --- Defaults for nuclear_params_ChPT_sigmapiN parameters
nuclear_params_ChPT_sigmapiN_scan.yaml               --- Defaults for nuclear_params_ChPT_sigmapiN parameters in DMEFT scans
nuclear_params_ChPT_sigmapiN_postprocessing.yaml     --- Defaults for nuclear_params_ChPT_sigmapiN parameters in postprocessing of DMEFT scans
cosmo_nuisance_Planck_lite_flat.yaml                 --- Nuisance parameters for Planck Lite likelihood, flat prior
cosmo_nuisance_Planck_lite_gauss.yaml                --- Nuisance parameters for Planck Lite likelihood, gaussian prior
cosmo_nuisance_Planck_TT_flat.yaml                   --- Nuisance parameters for Planck TT likelihood, flat prior
cosmo_nuisance_Planck_TT_gauss.yaml                  --- Nuisance parameters for Planck TT likelihood, gaussian prior
cosmo_nuisance_Planck_TTTEEE_flat.yaml               --- Nuisance parameters for Planck TTTEEE likelihood, flat prior
cosmo_nuisance_Planck_TTTEEE_gauss.yaml              --- Nuisance parameters for Planck TTTEEE likelihood, gaussian prior


Files used for unit testing
---------------------------

Found in the validation/ directory.
